;LMW human uPA/A145 was concentrated to 10 mg/ml
and incubated in 50 mM HEPES, 5.0 mM NaCl. pH 7.0,
5.0 mM thieno[2,3-b]pyridine-2-carboxamidine for 15 min on ice. 
The complex was crystallized by vapor diffusion in hanging 
drops containing equal volumes of protein-inhibitor solution 
(0.28 mM uPA/A145, 1.4 mM inhibitor and well solution
(20 % 2-propanol, 20 % PEG 4K, 100 mM sodium citrate, 
pH 6.5) sealed over the well.
;
